# Course Structure

## Role of the Teacher

#### All lessons within the Data Science unit are intended to be **facilitated by a teacher**. These lessons are **not designed as self-paced experiences for students** to work through at their own pace.


## Lessons
#### The lessons are designed for **45-minute class periods**, but can be modified for longer or shorter class periods. Some lessons, such as project lessons, take multiple days to complete. Suggested times are included in each lesson plan.

### **Lesson Components**

